Cell.Text: Beg pardon. You dropped some armor over there. Don't s'pose you'd be minding if I helped myself to it?
Umm... hello. You dropped a piece armor over there. I was kind of hoping that I could, you know, have it?
You there. That armor you dropped. You meant to do that? Can I have it then?
Excuse me. I'm assuming that armor you got rid of wasn't an accident, but just in case, I wanted to make sure I could take it.
That armor you got rid of. I can have it, yeah?
Pardon. I saw you toss a piece of armor. You wouldn't be minding if I take it, then?
Couldn't help but notice, that uh, you a pitched some armor. Just wanted to check with you before I took it. Is that alright?
Hey. That armor. You got rid of it, yeah? I can take it, no problem?
If you're not going to be using that armor you dropped. Do you mind if I take it?
That's great. I owe you one. Thanks!
That's mighty fine of you. Thank you.
I knew it. Thanks. They'll think twice before messing with me when I'm wearing that!
Thanks! I'm going to go put it on right now!
That's great. I'm going go get it right now.
That's mighty big of you. Thank ya.
They won't won't be able to hurt me when I'm wearing that, will they? Thanks! Bye.
Ta-da! I'm going be so tough when I'm wearing that. Look out. Here I come!
I'm going to go get it right now and wear it. Many thanks!
Oh. Well, then you should probably go get it before someone steals it.
What? Well... then you probably should go collect it before someone else does, shouldn't you?
Meh. I didn't want it anyway.
Oh... well. Never mind then.
Then what did you drop it for? You're not very smart. Anyone can just come and take it. You should go pick it up before that happens.
You dropped it by mistake? Well, if I was you, I'd go grab it now before somebody does.
Aww. I thought you were done with it. Tch. Can't win 'em all, can you. You better go pick that up. Someone might steal it.
Huh? Well... fine. I wasn't really gonna do anything with it anyway. Hmph.
Well, if you aim to keep it, you better go pick it up before someone snatches it.
